AUDIO: 'So, here we have everything that I was talking about. Our readme file is actually our own landing page inside of our GitHub repo and we can see here the image. So, image should be something'

[05:33] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'that is telling what is your project actually about. It\'s not just about putting a fancy image, so be careful with that one. Especially if you have some attractive thing like UI library, you want to show all those niceties that'

[05:46] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'you have inside of your library and show them right here in this image. It can be a screenshot or just like some kind of mix of all of your components. Then we have here nice looking badges. You can'

